which gives us the power to act - by left
side we desire and by using the right side,

00:00:37.400 --> 00:00:43.720
the power of pingala nadi, we act.

00:00:43.720 --> 00:00:48.840
I was telling you about the right side the
other day.

00:00:48.840 --> 00:00:54.300
Let us see how our right side is built up.

