I’m sorry for people who have come for the
first time but every time when I start the

00:01:00.590 --> 00:01:06.580
introduction to the subject, again it becomes
the same but later on I’ll explain to you

00:01:06.580 --> 00:01:09.080
about Sahaja.

00:01:09.080 --> 00:01:26.659
Now this right side pingala nadi is a very,
very important energy-giving energy

00:01:26.659 --> 00:01:30.150
which makes us act and activate.

00:01:30.150 --> 00:01:38.210
Now this one is made of all the five elements.

00:01:38.210 --> 00:01:46.070
You know all the five elements that have created
our physical being and our mental being.

00:01:46.070 --> 00:01:57.060
That’s how it helps us to work out all our
physical and mental problems, mental activities

00:01:57.060 --> 00:02:00.070
and mental and physical growth.

00:02:00.070 --> 00:02:14.680
Now this being made by those five elements,
when first time human beings started thinking

00:02:14.680 --> 00:02:27.859
of doing some action about anything, say in
India, they first thought why not somehow

00:02:27.859 --> 00:02:37.760
or other reach to the principle of these elements,
which is beyond physics, which is beyond chemistry.

00:02:37.760 --> 00:02:51.931
And to reach to that point, they thought it
would be better if we try to invoke or to

00:02:51.931 --> 00:02:59.319
awaken the Deities which are governing those
five elements.

00:02:59.319 --> 00:03:04.180
This was a very big mistake though, I should
say.

00:03:04.180 --> 00:03:11.839
Because human beings, whatever they take up,
they do not know where to stop.

00:03:11.839 --> 00:03:20.569
If you tell them that you have to clean your
teeth everyday, then they’ll go on cleaning

00:03:20.569 --> 00:03:23.879
it 12 times in 12 hours.

00:03:23.879 --> 00:03:31.939
You tell them anything, they’ll go so far
that they will destroy the instrument which

00:03:31.939 --> 00:03:33.729
is suppose to be looked after.

00:03:33.729 --> 00:03:39.720
That’s the nature of human beings, they
cannot have brakes to themselves.

00:03:39.720 --> 00:03:46.720
They do not have common sense as far as balance
in their life.

00:03:46.720 --> 00:03:59.290
So anything you give them, they become so
mad after it that in Marathi there is a word

00:03:59.290 --> 00:04:04.369
is that they ultimately put ashes on their
head, to say to declare that I am dead now,

00:04:04.369 --> 00:04:05.390
I’ve become ashes.

00:04:05.390 --> 00:04:14.680
Like that, they get so frantic that even while
doing this awakening of these principles,

00:04:14.680 --> 00:04:21.319
they forgot, lost their sight that we are
after all spirit and not these elements.

00:04:21.319 --> 00:04:23.180
We are beyond that.

00:04:23.180 --> 00:04:25.090
You have to reach beyond that.

00:04:25.090 --> 00:04:34.419
All these elements are only useful for us
to achieve a state in which we can create

00:04:34.419 --> 00:04:46.330
things and we can have more time to devote
to meditation to enjoy our self-realisation.

00:04:46.330 --> 00:04:57.270
They got completely blinded by the advances
they made on this side which is in pure and

00:04:57.270 --> 00:05:00.849
simple words is materialism.

00:05:00.849 --> 00:05:06.229
They became so responsible, so efficient.

00:05:06.229 --> 00:05:15.490
First in the Vedas, it’s written, the first
stanza is such that by reading these Vedas,

00:05:15.490 --> 00:05:22.849
if you do not know your spirit then it is
absolutely useless.

00:05:22.849 --> 00:05:26.680
But this stanza they always close down I think.

00:05:26.680 --> 00:05:32.650
Then they started worshipping those Deities,
this, that, exciting them, doing all ritualism,

00:05:32.650 --> 00:05:37.290
and all that and they just went into it headlong,
absolutely headlong.

00:05:37.290 --> 00:05:39.510
They would not turn back.

00:05:39.510 --> 00:05:47.949
So by exciting these elements, they discovered
the principles of these elements.

00:05:47.949 --> 00:05:53.890
For example, they discovered that gravity
is the essence of the Mother Earth.

00:05:53.890 --> 00:05:57.469
But it is not.

00:05:57.469 --> 00:05:59.830
That is not the essence of the Mother Earth.

00:05:59.830 --> 00:06:06.990
That is the energy that is asserted by Her
but Her essence is Her fragrance.

00:06:06.990 --> 00:06:15.659
They could not cross that limit where they
could see really the subtle thing which was

00:06:15.659 --> 00:06:19.930
the subtle principle of this energy of gravity
is the fragrance.

00:06:19.930 --> 00:06:28.419
All the fragrances come from Her.

00:06:28.419 --> 00:06:31.830
Of course man made there are, that’s different.

00:06:31.830 --> 00:06:37.199
But even the man made, are also coming from
Her, if you go trace the source, it’s up

00:06:37.199 --> 00:06:39.949
to the point, it is from there.

00:06:39.949 --> 00:06:48.310
Like that they went on discovering the subtler,
so called subtler energies or the principles

00:06:48.310 --> 00:06:53.300
of these elements from the Vedas style.

00:06:53.300 --> 00:06:55.900
Then it became a science.

00:06:55.900 --> 00:07:02.139
People started studying physics, chemistry,
this, that, understanding what was there before

00:07:02.139 --> 00:07:07.610
them, by going into it and trying to find
out what is it made of.

00:07:07.610 --> 00:07:16.749
For example, they went into atoms, they went
into say molecules and things and they tried

00:07:16.749 --> 00:07:26.810
to find out and there they find the oscillation
of the protons and they find the oscillation

00:07:26.810 --> 00:07:29.210
of these atoms.

00:07:29.210 --> 00:07:35.610
And they just can’t understand, from where
does this energy of this oscillation is coming.

00:07:35.610 --> 00:07:43.509
They could not capture that energy so they
thought better use the energy, so they started

00:07:43.509 --> 00:07:45.729
using the energy.

00:07:45.729 --> 00:07:51.120
Now it has gone to such a limit of the whole
thing is, now I read, saw that microchips

00:07:51.120 --> 00:07:52.689
or something coming up.

00:07:52.689 --> 00:08:00.129
After some time you won’t be using hands
or head or anything, it will be that microchips

00:08:00.129 --> 00:08:01.330
will be going on.

00:08:01.330 --> 00:08:05.930
But with this kind of a thing, with this extreme
behaviour, you’ll become a machine yourself.

00:08:05.930 --> 00:08:08.340
A slave of the machine.

00:08:08.340 --> 00:08:13.629
Today the petrol is exhausted, tomorrow electricity
is exhausted, then what are you going to do?

00:08:13.629 --> 00:08:17.080
You don’t know even to count two plus two.

00:08:17.080 --> 00:08:22.770
So you are left without any counting, you’ll
become the same primitive man and I don’t

00:08:22.770 --> 00:08:29.590
know what you will be doing, climbing on the
trees and living like monkeys, I don’t know

00:08:29.590 --> 00:08:31.249
what will happen.

00:08:31.249 --> 00:08:36.409
So all these advancement that you did has
gone too far.

00:08:36.409 --> 00:08:43.529
But as a result of too much efficiency, too
much responsibility and all that, you became

00:08:43.529 --> 00:08:49.860
sort of addicted to it and then with that
you started dominating other people.

00:08:49.860 --> 00:08:55.541
The machinery came in, that you produced such
a lot of machinery style that you didn’t

00:08:55.541 --> 00:09:00.570
know what to do so you had to find out markets
where you sell them so you started capturing

00:09:00.570 --> 00:09:04.970
other markets where you started selling them
and that’s how all these economic problems

00:09:04.970 --> 00:09:06.350
and all this have started.

00:09:06.350 --> 00:09:10.540
There are developing countries, there are
developed countries, all things going on in

00:09:10.540 --> 00:09:12.060
this mad world.

00:09:12.060 --> 00:09:19.620
But we reach a point now where we realise
that this machine has done something nonsensical

00:09:19.620 --> 00:09:20.620
within us.

00:09:20.620 --> 00:09:25.910
When we reach that point, we start thinking
now what are we to do.

00:09:25.910 --> 00:09:33.769
We have been very responsible, not you people
but your forefathers may be, who went to fight

00:09:33.769 --> 00:09:39.860
the whole world and do this and they had to
be at right time at right places and do all

00:09:39.860 --> 00:09:41.209
sorts of things.

00:09:41.209 --> 00:09:47.580
By that over-responsibility you became sort
of fed up, you just didn’t know what to

00:09:47.580 --> 00:09:48.580
do.

00:09:48.580 --> 00:09:50.770
For example, morning you wear a grey suit,
in the night you have to wear a tail coat

00:09:50.770 --> 00:09:57.100
and then if you have to drink your wine, you
have to take a separate glass and for that

00:09:57.100 --> 00:09:58.100
this.

00:09:58.100 --> 00:10:03.290
It became too much messy you said “Throw
them in the sea”.

00:10:03.290 --> 00:10:10.709
We have collected all this nonsense, we have
collected all these forms and horrible things

00:10:10.709 --> 00:10:12.750
that have made us so rigid.

00:10:12.750 --> 00:10:16.899
That’s how you try to throw away everything
but even then when you throw away, where do

00:10:16.899 --> 00:10:17.899
you go?

00:10:17.899 --> 00:10:19.750
I mean you have to exist, you cannot just
hang in the air.

00:10:19.750 --> 00:10:21.890
So you said now take another style.

00:10:21.890 --> 00:10:26.260
And another style is even worse, much worse.

00:10:26.260 --> 00:10:35.590
Because then no responsibility, no respect,
no understanding, so this power goes absolutely

00:10:35.590 --> 00:10:36.590
zero.

00:10:36.590 --> 00:10:39.899
You are tired very soon.

00:10:39.899 --> 00:10:46.880
I’ve seen, I mean in the BBC and all that,
young people, I’m a very old woman compared

00:10:46.880 --> 00:10:50.730
to them, after saying two three words, they
say “Ahhh”, they go down.

00:10:50.730 --> 00:10:52.209
Again after saying something, “Ahhh”.

00:10:52.209 --> 00:10:54.279
This is very big acting these days.

00:10:54.279 --> 00:10:57.630
In any play you see a person saying, “Ahhh”.

00:10:57.630 --> 00:11:04.170
What does it take to act for this kind of
a thing.

00:11:04.170 --> 00:11:06.540
This is what is very common.

00:11:06.540 --> 00:11:09.209
Now you notice, the reason is you are tired.

00:11:09.209 --> 00:11:11.380
You’re absolutely tired, why?

00:11:11.380 --> 00:11:23.320
Because your brain is the same old brain and
you have taken a new life, you cannot adjust

00:11:23.320 --> 00:11:24.730
yourself to that.

00:11:24.730 --> 00:11:29.290
You say that now I am sitting down, doing
nothing, I am not going to be efficient anymore

00:11:29.290 --> 00:11:33.880
and all that, I’m sitting down, the brain
is going, chug-chug-chug-chug-chug, morning

00:11:33.880 --> 00:11:34.880
till evening.

00:11:34.880 --> 00:11:36.120
How to stop this brain?

00:11:36.120 --> 00:11:41.370
This brain is working so hard, using up all
your energy, you have no strength.

00:11:41.370 --> 00:11:48.139
So to counteract you will say let’s take
to some sort of a thing by which we go out

00:11:48.139 --> 00:11:49.389
of this madness.

00:11:49.389 --> 00:11:56.269
Let’s take to something that takes you as
we call it the right or the left side, take

00:11:56.269 --> 00:12:03.630
something like say hashish, or something like
another thing, LSD, to go to the right or

00:12:03.630 --> 00:12:04.690
to the left.

00:12:04.690 --> 00:12:08.910
Now what happens with that you know very well.

00:12:08.910 --> 00:12:15.070
Now thank God you have realised also to that
was nonsensical action, that was wrong.

00:12:15.070 --> 00:12:20.160
These are two areas within us which are called
as Adi Bhautik and Adi Devik.

00:12:20.160 --> 00:12:28.790
Now the Adi Bhautik are the ones which take
you to the left side is the subconscious and

00:12:28.790 --> 00:12:34.680
the Adi Devik are the ones where you try to
invoke the devas and all that on the right

00:12:34.680 --> 00:12:42.269
hand side, that one is the Adi Devik where
we call it supra-conscious area.

00:12:42.269 --> 00:12:47.230
These two are of no use to human beings, actually.

00:12:47.230 --> 00:12:49.750
They are not meant for human beings.

00:12:49.750 --> 00:12:57.050
They are meant for people who are dead, who
are dead souls, who are good for nothing.

00:12:57.050 --> 00:12:58.720
Now they cannot get realisation.

00:12:58.720 --> 00:13:00.910
It’s not meant for you.

00:13:00.910 --> 00:13:04.209
That’s the area you should not reside.

00:13:04.209 --> 00:13:08.110
But you enter into these areas because of
extreme natures.

00:13:08.110 --> 00:13:14.100
Some people by going into these drugs, some
taking to some sort of movements like mesmerisms,

00:13:14.100 --> 00:13:16.740
spiritualisms and all sorts of isms.

00:13:16.740 --> 00:13:24.990
Some people onto the right hand side like
taking to what you call these people who are

00:13:24.990 --> 00:13:30.090
racialists and all such organisations which
are racialist and this and that and you know

00:13:30.090 --> 00:13:33.000
all that kind of a people, like Hitlerish
type.

00:13:33.000 --> 00:13:38.410
All this is nothing but is a kind of intoxicant
which makes you forget the reality, that you

00:13:38.410 --> 00:13:46.339
are a human being, that you have to become
the spirit, that you are the spirit is the

00:13:46.339 --> 00:13:47.339
reality.

00:13:47.339 --> 00:13:55.990
Now the present trend in the Western life
is very much set in this country about which

00:13:55.990 --> 00:13:57.700
I am very much concerned.

