Why they have taken this course, I don’t
know.

00:14:26.800 --> 00:14:30.450
Now to do any work, also they’re frightened.

00:14:30.450 --> 00:14:36.269
Supposing we put this colour, then it may
not match, it doesn’t matter, doesn’t

00:14:36.269 --> 00:14:37.269
matter.

