What does it matter?

00:14:38.329 --> 00:14:43.620
Because of those previous ideas they are so
frightened of doing anything, though they

00:14:43.620 --> 00:14:51.660
say they have broken all those ideas and they
have taken to new liberated ways and all that.

00:14:51.660 --> 00:14:57.110
