or take a hooligan, or take a robber or anyone

00:15:51.100 --> 00:15:57.160
who has appeared on the newspaper as if they
have drunk all the newspaper into their memory.

00:15:57.160 --> 00:16:04.040
The whole thing is so clear cut in their mind
that is sometimes, I mean.

00:16:04.040 --> 00:16:13.970
But if you tell them to fix one chair, never
trust that chair (everyone laughing).

00:16:13.970 --> 00:16:14.970
